Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Starck Real Estate

data.description: Beautiful spacious home in The Sonatas of Woodstock.  The open concept design includes the family room, kitchen, and eating area. The large kitchen has a spacious peninsula, stainless steel appliances, large pantry and plenty of counterspace.  The eating area looks out to the beautiful views of open farmland behind the home and the sliding glass door opens to a spacious deck for entertaining.  The master bedroom on the 2nd floor has a private bath and 2 walk-in closets. The second level includes 4 additional large bedrooms, a loft and a full bath. The 3-car tandem garage provides ample storage space and a full basement awaits your finishing touches. This home has had a lot of upgrades.  Walking distance to Woodstock North High School and Merryman baseball fields.  Close to Woodstock Square Historic District, shopping and restaurants.
